---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Horse Show Golf Cart Rentals Ocala | Equestrian Event Transportation | Ocala Golf Carts">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 to-emerald-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        Horse Show Golf Cart Rentals Ocala
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-emerald-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Navigate Ocala's premier equestrian venues with ease. Our reliable golf cart rentals are perfect for horse shows, competitors, and spectators.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Rental Options -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Our Fleet</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-6">Perfect Carts for Every Equestrian Need</h2>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">Choose from our range of gas-powered golf carts, ideal for navigating large showgrounds and transporting gear.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- 2-Passenger Cart -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 border border-emerald-100">
          <img src="/golf cart images/4-passenger-golf-cart-ocala.jpg" alt="2-Passenger Golf Cart for Horse Shows in Ocala" class="rounded-t-2xl w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-3">2-Passenger Cart</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Great for individuals or couples needing quick transport around the showgrounds.</p>
            <ul class="text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-emerald-500 mr-2"></i>Gas-powered reliability</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-emerald-500 mr-2"></i>Compact and agile</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-emerald-500 mr-2"></i>Easy parking</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-4">Call for Pricing</p>
              <a href="tel:+13527801526" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-emerald-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:from-emerald-700 hover:to-emerald-800 transition-all duration-300 shadow-md">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-phone mr-2"></i>Get Quote
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 4-Passenger Cart -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 border border-emerald-100">
          <img src="/golf cart images/4-passenger-golf-cart-rental.jpg" alt="4-Passenger Golf Cart for Horse Shows - Ideal for Teams and Families" class="rounded-t-2xl w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-3">4-Passenger Cart</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Ideal for families, small teams, or transporting judges and officials.</p>
            <ul class="text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-emerald-500 mr-2"></i>Gas-powered reliability</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-emerald-500 mr-2"></i>Comfortable seating</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-emerald-500 mr-2"></i>Ample space for gear</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-4">Call for Pricing</p>
              <a href="tel:+13527801526" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-emerald-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:from-emerald-700 hover:to-emerald-800 transition-all duration-300 shadow-md">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-phone mr-2"></i>Get Quote
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 6-Passenger Cart -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 border border-emerald-100">
          <img src="/golf cart images/6-passenger-golf-cart-rental.jpg" alt="6-Passenger Golf Cart for Horse Shows - Perfect for Large Groups" class="rounded-t-2xl w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-3">6-Passenger Cart</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Best for larger groups, shuttling spectators, or extensive equipment transport.</p>
            <ul class="text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-emerald-500 mr-2"></i>Gas-powered reliability</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-emerald-500 mr-2"></i>High capacity</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-emerald-500 mr-2"></i>Robust for all terrains</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-4">Call for Pricing</p>
              <a href="tel:+13527801526" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-emerald-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:from-emerald-700 hover:to-emerald-800 transition-all duration-300 shadow-md">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-phone mr-2"></i>Get Quote
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-emerald-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Benefits</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-6">Why Rent for Your Next Horse Show?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 mb-12">Our golf carts offer convenience, efficiency, and comfort for any equestrian event.</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-emerald-100">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-horse text-emerald-600 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-3">Easy Venue Navigation</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Effortlessly move between arenas, stables, and vendor areas without tiring yourself out.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-emerald-100">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-suitcase-rolling text-emerald-600 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-3">Gear Transport</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Spacious carts make it simple to transport saddles, tack, feed, and other essential equipment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-emerald-100">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-users text-emerald-600 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-3">Guest & Staff Shuttle</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Provide comfortable transport for your team, family, or event attendees across large properties.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-700 to-emerald-900 text-white py-16 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Planning for Your Next Horse Show?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-emerald-100 mb-8">Get a reliable golf cart rental for a smooth and successful event. Contact us for a quote!</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="tel:+13527801526" class="bg-white text-emerald-700 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-300 shadow-lg">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-phone mr-2"></i>
          Call (352) 780-1526
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors duration-300">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope mr-2"></i>
          Email Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
